            "text": "Yes. Inspector Roofing serves homeowners, HOAs, property managers, and commercial property owners around Downtown Ball Ground, Ball Ground Highway, Howell Bridge Road, Calvin Farmer Park, I-575, and the North Cherokee foothills."
